{"tid":1298142,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"醉漢扯少女口罩　群警袖手","createTime":"2019-07-08T19:24:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T20:18:47.000Z","uid":240362,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"0181c6a03c1cf47a9d005a89e797dd0a847dcaf8","tid":1298142,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T19:24:07.000Z","msg":"【本報訊】警察濫暴亦縱暴，冷眼旁觀醉漢傷人。前晚警方驅散旺角示威者，午夜時分仍有少量示威者於西洋菜南街及亞皆老街交界聚集，有一名中年醉漢出現襲擊示威者。據在場的葵青區區議員周偉雄指，該醉漢突然襲擊在場人士，並釀成衝突，醉漢突倒地流鼻血。他與同行社工欲上前協助時，亦遭醉漢掌摑，眼鏡橫飛，醉漢隨後襲擊現場女士，抓住少女手腕，試圖除去其口罩。<br />\n<br />\n周偉雄表示，施襲地點約五呎外便有十多名警員，在場市民及立法會議員許智峯曾要求警員協助，但有關警員未有理會，袖手旁觀，「咁樣真係好唔合理，見到市民之間有紛爭，連帶走醉酒鬧事嘅人、分隔兩邊嘅人都唔肯」。最終鬧事醉漢混亂中倒地，被送上救護車離開。<br />\n<br />\n少女憂報案「告返轉頭」<br />\n被襲的口罩少女張小姐指，當晚用膳後路經該地，見醉漢鬧事，「個男人見到人就揮拳打人，佢無啦啦捉住另一個女仔，我想去拉開佢哋」，隨後被醉漢抓住其手腕，並將其穿戴的口罩扯下。她又稱，「由見到警察清場開始已經好驚，之後又有咁嘅衝突，一路都好驚」。對於十多名警員未有阻止施襲男子，張小姐表示失望，「佢哋係一啲行動都冇」，但未考慮好報警，「唔夠膽，驚會俾人告返轉頭」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190709/20723979\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190709%2F20723979&d=Xf5vvBv8GY7fsWMyNBE0dqVJa0bF76%2FliPNifPMhSX0%3D&h=ee41a28e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190709%2F20723979&h=36a192b2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20190709/20723979</a>"},{"pid":"a142f9126c1d3933810bd97542231a13076854ca","tid":1298142,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T19:24:54.000Z","msg":"黑警廢老死全家"},{"pid":"c285aef00b1e82e62a9f2e317b4e9bf127b9ef54","tid":1298142,"uid":12609,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T19:26:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190709/large/a0204a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190709%2Flarge%2Fa0204a.gif&h=758f6f92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n起佢出黎"},{"pid":"dd2477973454b7893966acf1b9b2f3ee954f4165","tid":1298142,"uid":162783,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T19:26:27.000Z","msg":"以後唔洗報警 警察先最惡"},{"pid":"70c5eb1c35737d4dd610ffeef492ce1756906593","tid":1298142,"uid":41355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T19:27:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a719d1013acdc964924da4651e47792c7179d5cc","tid":1298142,"uid":23189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T19:28:42.000Z","msg":"睡前讀物 入嚟睇睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n「運動末來發展」我想分享少少意見同建議<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1295758\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1295758</a>"},{"pid":"a178f2f79dbf3539874186fbf526a6f6baff7645","tid":1298142,"uid":259613,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c285aef00b1e82e62a9f2e317b4e9bf127b9ef54","tid":1298142,"uid":12609,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T19:26:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190709/large/a0204a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190709%2Flarge%2Fa0204a.gif&h=758f6f92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n起佢出黎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T19:38:09.000Z","msg":"起到果個真係勁"},{"pid":"e87e709399bbc6935ed097c45f439de03559f8f6","tid":1298142,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd2477973454b7893966acf1b9b2f3ee954f4165","tid":1298142,"uid":162783,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T19:26:27.000Z","msg":"以後唔洗報警 警察先最惡"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T19:47:41.000Z","msg":"根本唔會再幫香港市民<br />\n份糧就拿足"},{"pid":"9fd9f954a8e91e9f3c94520beb50002b6c7f60f9","tid":1298142,"uid":156326,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T19:57:02.000Z","msg":"呢啲同埋放自己友嘅相係咪可以拎去警察非中立果邊做證據 取得佢地個獨立薪酬表"},{"pid":"19779a7e954e43fa53